This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) as it deals with machine translation and N-gram approximations. It could also belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) as these fields are closely related to NLP. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) could also be a possible sub-category as the paper deals with ranking of MT outputs. Deep Learning (cs.DL) could also be a possible sub-category as deep learning techniques are often used in NLP tasks.
